overview:
We are a online community that is centered around five crucial elements for long term business success:

1.) Business Advice

2.) Leadership Development

3.) Financial Advice

4.) Personal Development

5.) Marketing Advice

All five elements will help improve your skill set as a budding entrepreneur.

If you are on the fence about starting your own business venture or if you are stagnating with current business goals, we strongly believe in the importance of encouragement.

The Woman in Leadership blog community is a place to share your voice and to make it the go-to resource for female small business owners, work at home moms, and start-ups.

What is the Mission and Purpose of Woman in Leadership?

Our mission is to help you gain the priceless knowledge that is essential for becoming a successful entrepreneur and prominent leader in your industry.

Is the Woman in Leadership Online Community Right for Me?

The Woman in Leadership name stands for every entrepreneurial woman who is not afraid to pursue her dreams, no matter the obstacle.

If this sounds like you, then this is the right place for you!

Whether you are just starting out or are currently established, we provide you with a wealth of inspiration, motivation, financial, and business building advice.

We also offer affordable professional services for you and your growing business.

What Professional Services Does Woman in Leadership Offer?

The services offered by Woman in Leadership will change as the community continues to grow.

All services have been created to help you stay on the road to success with your home business, online business, startup, or established small business.

Our professional services include the following:

Consultation (2 Hours Free) Free Business Building Courses Free Marketing Courses Writing Requests (Blog content, ghostwriting, articles, etc.) Social Media Management and Marketing Advertising and Sponsorship Programs

For detailed information about each of the services we provide, just head on over to Our Services page.

ABOUT THE FOUNDER

Stacie Walker, the Editor-in-Chief and the company founder, is the the brainchild behind this fabulous community.

She officially said good-bye to her corporate job to build her own business from the comfort of her home in 2008.

She has NEVER looked back.

Stacie loves working with professional leaders and dedicated entrepreneurs in the small business, home business, and online business industries.

Known as a success-driven entrepreneur, it has been her mission and purpose to educate you on possessing the correct tools to establish a better business model and to assist you with improving the quality of your personal life.

A top priority of Stacie is to provide a comfortable place for the novice and the experienced entrepreneur to get a bit of inspiration, motivation, and business building strategies for long term success.

She believes all of the above elements are essential to improve your skill set as a budding entrepreneur in your industry.
